snippet.title: Gravewood High — Multiplayer Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Gravewood High welcomes you and your friends to solve its obscure mysteries and confront the mad teacher together. With dreadful terror, HeroCraft PC announces the much-requested multiplayer update is coming this summer! Play with up to five friends as you try to survive the monstrous Mr. Hyde. 

The multiplayer update is tied to the base game. Owners of Gravewood High will be able to play multiplayer at no additional cost. Get Gravewood High today → https://bit.ly/GHighMulti
